manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: The SmartyPants Difference Premiumt Ingredients Our approach to science-based nutrition delivers the highest-quality ingredients available in forms that your body prefers and can easily use. So you get more of the nutrients you want - all in one delicious gummy. Taste Because the best supplements are the ones you actually take. We make our gummies extra yummy with all-natural flavors derived from sources like spices, fruits, vegetables and/or herbs. No synthetic colors, artificial flavors or sweeteners.* *Claims verified by Regulatory Affairs, 2019 Free Of Only the best ingredients. No weird additives. SmartyPants are non-GMO, gluten-free and free of milk, eggs, shellfish, soy, peanuts, wheat, fish allergens and tree nut allergens.* This formula also received the Clean Label Project's Purity Award, the highest overall rating for product purity and value. *Claims verified by Regulatory Affairs, 2019

Because science never sleeps... Neither does our in-house team of nutritional scientists. We’re always learning, growing and innovating to create the best multifunctional supplements for your health - made with the most premium ingredients. To ensure our formulas can help offer a number of health benefits and fill a range of nutritional gaps, we base them on the latest science, current dietary patterns and recommendations from the Health and Medicine Division of the National Academies of Sciences (formerly the Institute of Medicine) and our Scientific Advisory board. That's the smarter way to healthier.

Targeted Nutrition for Women 50+ Gray hair don't care. From training for your next marathon to taking the grandkids on another adventure, you need a supplement that can keep up. That's why our Masters Formula Women 50+ is made with premium ingredients, that the body prefers and can easily use, to help fill nutritional gaps and help offer a number of health benefits too! We use the highest-quality ingredients available to deliver omega-3 EPA & DHA essential fatty acids (from fish oil) and support for your eye, bone, heart and immune health - all in one easy and delicious serving.* When it's time to master your health, we've got this! *These statements have not been evaluated by the FDA. *This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. **VitaCholine is a registered TM of Balchem Corporation. **Lutemax 2020 is a TM of OmniActive Health Technologies Ltd.

Omega-3 EPA/DHA Time to seas the day with omega-3 (EPA & DHA). We source ours from sustainable stocks of wild-caught small fish (anchovies, sardines, herring, and mackerel) to deliver a high-quality source of essential fatty acids. Lutein and Zeaxanthin Set your sights high with lutein and zeaxanthin (Lutemax 2020** from marigold flowers) for eye health.* These nutrients help improve visual performance and support the eyes' ability to see distant objects more clearly.* CoQ10 Let’s have a heart to heart (about your health). Your body makes CoQ10, but the amount it produces declines with age. So, we include CoQ10 to support cardiovascular health.* Vitamin B12 Be ready for whatever life throws at you with vitamin B12 to support energy metabolism. We include this B vitamin because it's what the body prefers.

Vitamin K No bones about it. We include vitamin K in the premium form K2 (MK7) for bone health. Vitamin K helps your body utilize calcium and magnesium from your diet, to support bone health.* Folate We include folate in the premium form methylfolate to help form red blood cells.* Methylfolate is the active form your body prefers because it doesn’t need to be converted before your body can use it. Vitamin C When it comes to antioxidants, our upgraded formula is high in vitamin C for the maintenance of good health. It also supports collagen formation and helps the body metabolize fats and proteins.* Choline Liver your best life! Our premium formula includes the essential nutrient choline, as VitaCholine, to support liver function. It also helps support cell structure and integrity.**

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars First vitamin I'll actually take
reviews.reviewText: Other vitamins make me really queasy so I wouldn't take them, but these don't bother me at all, and they're delicious. The last visit with my doctor all my vitamin levels were appropriate (which has never happened before) so these must be working! I'm glad Amazon sells this 50+ formula because it's not sold in stores near me. It's literally the first vitamin I'm happy to take. It's very easy way to get the nutrients you need as you get older.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars the flavors listed are not the flavors I got
reviews.reviewText: Just started taking them so I don't know how well they work or if they will make a difference but I am so disappointed in the flavor! If they work well I will choke them down but the flavors listed here are lemon, orange and blueberry but on the bottle the flavors are blueberry, orange creme, and strawberry banana. I HATE banana flavor. If I had known this was one of them I would never had bought them. If they do make a difference physically I will have to try a different version and hope that the flavors listed are correct.

Very tasty with different fruit flavours, while giving me the necessary supplements. Like it very much as the gummy dissolves easily which does not irritate my guts as compared to others that comes in solid tablets.
